                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d034"><locus target="#59r"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1075PresentationJesus"/> before two saintly elders. The text at the top of the folio is not a caption, but rather an excerpt from Dǝggwa by Saint Yared on Great Thursday and the washing of the disciples’ feet</desc></decoNote>
